{"TopicId":158633,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Kerbals in VAB and SPH","CreatedByName":"2ARM2","CreatedById":176470,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-03T10:38:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"2ARM2","CreatedById":176470,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-03T10:38:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy game runs fine when i\u0027m building but when the kerbals walking around get in my fov it seems to lag quite a bit. Is there anyway to remove/lower the amount of kerbals with mods or settings?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tr1gg3r","CreatedById":161427,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-03T10:58:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYer theres a setting to turn off \u0027ground crew\u0027 somewhere in the settings options.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jros83","CreatedById":118956,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-03T11:31:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223007756\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022158633\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221491217080\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161427\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tr1gg3r\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n32 minutes ago, Tr1gg3r said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYer theres a setting to turn off \u0027ground crew\u0027 somewhere in the settings options.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis. It\u0027s on the very first page of settings, top-left side, either first or second option. You can turn the little clones off.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"2ARM2","CreatedById":176470,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-03T23:48:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThx\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"egoego","CreatedById":138988,